      customization in our labeling solutions for diverse applications, from
      industrial to commercial.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl z-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 pt-14 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"
  >
    <div
      class="whyus-card rounded-lg border border-2 border-sky-200 p-8 text-center shadow transition duration-300 hover:scale-105"
    >
      <div
        class="img mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md"
      >
        <img src="img/icons/quality.png" alt="" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-6 text-slate-500 text-lg font-bold">
        Commitment to Quality
      </h3>
      <p
        class="my-4 mb-0 font-normal leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-slate-500"
